    "Therefore, we exclude these anomaly-free sequences from consideration.",
    "Due to the fact that the original implementation of TODS sometimes generates anomalies that do not match their specified anomaly types (e.g., constructing trend and seasonal anomalies may result in obvious global outliers), we modify the anomaly generation code in TODS to ensure that the injected anomalies align more closely with their defined types.",
    "It is worth noting that we aggregate the overall evaluation at the dataset level instead of the curve level because the imbalance in sample sizes across different datasets can lead to biased results.",
